name: TOP OF THE CHOPS
description:
MARY DOLL IS CERTAINLY TOP OF THE CHOPS!
COLOURFULLY VIBRANT ILLUSTRATED DIGITAL PRINT TEE USING SUPER SOFT JERSEY COTTON THAT IS KIND AND COSY FOR YOUR LITTLE ONES SKIN.
WE ARE DOWN WITH THE SPROGS! WE KNOW THROUGH EXPERIENCE THAT KIDS DON'T LIKE LABELS SO WE HAVE LEFT THEM OUT AND WE USE IRON IN LABELS INSTEAD - JUST SO THEY DON'T IRRITATE OR ANNOY.
THIS TEE IS SUPER SOFT 100% JERSEY COTTON
MACHINE WASHABLE
OUR IMAGERY WILL LAST AS LONG AS THE T-SHIRT FITS AND IT WON'T FADE NEITHER.
YOU CAN WASH THIS FUN TEE AT 30 DEGREES AND WE DON'T RECOMMEND TUMBLE DRYING AS WITH IT BEING JERSEY COTTON THEY TEND TO SHRINK. SO JUST WASH ON 30 AND HANG TO DRY.
FINALLY WARM IRON. NOT TOO HOT!

YOUR LITTLE ONE WILL LOVE THE FEEL OF THIS TEE AGAINST THEIR SKIN, ITS A TOUCHY FEELY TEE INDEED!

AVAILABLE IN A LONG SLEEVE TOO!
